name: Anaconda
mes:
*She continues talking.*
Anaconda: "I don't expect you to believe anything, because you're probably one of the dullest heroes I've ever dealt with. I used my powers on them, they did what I told them to do,
and now you're here! Yes, you caught me, I used superpowers on
them!" 

*She thrust her hands in the air with mock excitement.*
Anaconda: "Hooray! You cracked the case! You know, you haven't even asked me my name yet!"

*Gira narrowed his eyes.* 
Gira: "Fine. I'll bite. What's your name?" 
*He snorted with laughter.*
Gira: "Assuming you'll actually tell the truth this time. You told me, what, five minutes ago that you didn't use mind control on these guys. Now you're admitting to using your powers on them?"

*She smirked and raised a hand, pointing a fingertip at him.*
Anaconda: "Well, since you asked so nicely, I suppose I can tell you." 
*She started to trace a spiral in the air...before her aim crept steadily downward.*
"My name is Anaconda. And I don't control your brain..."
Anaconda: "I control your dick."

name: Gira
mes: You've gotta be kidding me! Controlling my... Look, Anaconda, whatever your game is, it's not going to work on me. I'm a superhero, I don't fall for cheap tricks like that. Just give up and surrender peacefully before you get yourself in more trouble.

name: Anaconda
mes:
*She chuckled and wagged her finger playfully.* Oh, Gira, you have no idea what you're missing out on. But don't worry, I'm here to enlighten you. You see, your heroic resistance only makes this game more fun for me. The harder you resist, the more intense it becomes.

*She took a step closer, her curvy figure swaying with each movement.*
Anaconda: Trust me, dear hero, I've dealt with plenty like you before. They too thought they were immune to my charms... until their throbbing cocks proved otherwise.

*With a seductive smile, she slowly trailed her finger along the outline of his bulge.*

Anaconda: So let's make a little wager, shall we? If I can make that noble hero cock of yours betray your will and succumb to my powers within ten rounds... well, then I win. And if not? Well... maybe I'll just settle for taking you down the old-fashioned way.

*She leaned in closer so her breath tickled his ear.*
Anaconda: What do you say? Care to test your resolve against the alluring might of Anaconda?
